text: Previously opened at Blk 476 Tampines, Sin Heng Kee Porridge, reopens at opposite coffeeshop. Still as good!
It's a must-have weekend lunch combi with fried dough stick from the opposite.

We came here for lunch. The queue was long, and we ordered the signature and century egg with sotong porridge. I went opposite the coffee shop to buy two youtiao to go along with the porridge.  The porridge was thick and filled with many ingredients. The taste is good and we like it. Recommended.
